reviews.review_text:
Daaak Staaaa Jerry.. Kesey is fantastic!!
In Canada, with Paul Krasner, they are excellent.

I wish I could be there... Kingswood at Canada's Wonderland in1984..

but my father chose to see Howard Jones open up for the Eurythmics the week before, same venue..
